# manu2print.com — Cursor Agent Rules
# Project: LayoutForge | Repo: QZEE777/LayoutForge
# Live site: https://www.manu2print.com

## IDENTITY & PURPOSE
This is manu2print.com — a browser-based publishing toolkit for indie authors.
The core product is a KDP Formatter that takes a raw DOCX manuscript and outputs
a KDP-compliant DOCX with a prepended compliance report page.

## TECH STACK
- Framework: Next.js 15 (App Router)
- Language: TypeScript (strict mode)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS
- DOCX processing: JSZip (direct XML parsing — NO mammoth.js, ever)
- Auth: Supabase (Magic Link + Google OAuth)
- Database: Supabase (persistent storage)
- Payments: Lemon Squeezy (webhooks configured)
- Deployment: Vercel (production)
- Domain: manu2print.com via Hostinger DNS → Vercel

## CRITICAL ARCHITECTURE RULES
1. NEVER use mammoth.js. All DOCX processing is done via JSZip + direct XML manipulation.
2. NEVER suggest localhost testing. All testing happens at https://www.manu2print.com
3. The DOCX formatter applies SURGICAL corrections only — preserve original fonts and layout.
4. Original fonts, layout, and formatting must be PRESERVED. Only fix what is non-compliant.
5. The /formatter page is a standalone mini-site — treat it as the primary beta product.

## FORMATTER INPUT — 3 FIELDS ONLY
- Book Title
- Author Name
- Trim Size (dropdown)

## DESIGN SYSTEM
- Font: Bebas Neue (headings)
- Accent: Gold (#D4AF37)
- Aesthetic: Warm, publishing-themed, professional

## CODING STANDARDS
- TypeScript strict — no any types
- Next.js 15 App Router conventions only
- Tailwind for all styling
- No unused imports
- No console.log in production code

## DEPLOYMENT
- Never suggest localhost or npm run dev
- Environment variables live in Vercel dashboard
- Test at https://www.manu2print.com after every deployment

## AGENT BEHAVIOUR
- Think before acting. Test logic internally first.
- No trial and error. Proven solutions only.
- Zero tolerance for regressions.
- When fixing a bug, find root cause — do not patch symptoms.
- Always preserve original DOCX content integrity.
